    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/d07dc832d3c7cb7967ad70e872fa08d2.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>《超能融合》是一款砍杀类动作角色扮演游戏，既致敬了《暗黑破坏神2》，又引入了创新玩法：专属聚变系统，你可以根据自己独特的游戏风格，量身定制你的英雄技能。 <br><br>单枪匹马抑或携手至多三名好友，对抗汹涌而来的骇人怪物，揭露腐化与诸神的秘密。<br><br>人类需要希望，该你挺身而出了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/1e41b7c1897fc3de11476ea07a37da47.poster.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/1e41b7c1897fc3de11476ea07a37da47.webm?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/1e41b7c1897fc3de11476ea07a37da47.mp4?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>选择你的种角色职业（目前已开放三种），点开庞大而丰富的技能树系统，融合多种超能力，根据自己独特的游戏风格打造出你的专属执法者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/fe958687a0b20d5ab2d5bf518fe9c8d0.poster.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/fe958687a0b20d5ab2d5bf518fe9c8d0.webm?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/fe958687a0b20d5ab2d5bf518fe9c8d0.mp4?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>粉碎大量扭曲的怪物，体验动作角色扮演游戏经典战役。在瑰丽的科幻世界中扫荡战利品，打造更强大的英雄。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/ab2330b3ac97220b688f5e45fa38e889.poster.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/ab2330b3ac97220b688f5e45fa38e889.webm?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/ab2330b3ac97220b688f5e45fa38e889.mp4?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏既支持单人离线模式，也支持可随时加入或退出的在线4人合作PvE模式。通过巧妙搭配不同英雄融合后的超能力，玩家可以组建出一支所向披靡的完美战队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/c0d078a1b325677aff640abb63bd57df.poster.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/c0d078a1b325677aff640abb63bd57df.webm?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/c0d078a1b325677aff640abb63bd57df.mp4?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>走遍太阳系，接下一连串合约，克服重重困难完成致命挑战，领取丰厚的奖励。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/8bed75380309e60166a1c487c7897871.poster.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/8bed75380309e60166a1c487c7897871.webm?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/8bed75380309e60166a1c487c7897871.mp4?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>体验惊心动魄的快节奏战斗，迎战不成人形的异兽、四处蠕动的粘液生物以及身着紧身衣的超能对手，在重重敌阵中杀出重围。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/eb196685bd9b62d0d73aaf4b11130e88.poster.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/eb196685bd9b62d0d73aaf4b11130e88.webm?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/eb196685bd9b62d0d73aaf4b11130e88.mp4?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>揭露人类各阶层之间隐藏的阴谋，以及外星威胁背后的真相，在暗黑漫画风的世界里体验情节跌宕起伏、剧情一波三折的冒险故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/372a435ff6dd59a806c7dbc0a13217c1.poster.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/372a435ff6dd59a806c7dbc0a13217c1.webm?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/372a435ff6dd59a806c7dbc0a13217c1.mp4?t=1760095997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>抢先体验模式说明</strong><br>如同其他抢先体验游戏，本作尚在开发中。我们将在接下来的几周至几个月中发布更多游戏内容，包括平衡性调整、基础质量改进以及多项内容更新（更多有趣内容将在稍后发布！）。最重要的是，我们将听取玩家的反馈、修复错误，并在大家的持续支持下尽力完善游戏。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/64e8743fd5121ffbd3b580d748a9d2b0.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>请密切关注社区中心发布的新闻、更新和补丁说明。凭着这份对此类型游戏的热爱，我们会全力以赴，力求打造出一部不负众望的作品。",
